Class RespondToBestOfferRequestType

java.lang.Object
  com.ebay.soap.eBLBaseComponents.AbstractRequestType
      com.ebay.soap.eBLBaseComponents.RespondToBestOfferRequestType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class RespondToBestOfferRequestType
extends AbstractRequestType
implements Serializable

Enables the seller of a Best Offer item to accept, decline, or counter offers made by bidders. Best offers can be declined in bulk, using the same message from the seller to the bidders of all rejected offers.

Java class for RespondToBestOfferRequestType complex type.
